Intro for the Network-Projects Folder
The Network-Projects folder serves as a centralized location for all packet capture (PCAP) datasets and their corresponding README documentation created throughout the semester. This folder is designed to keep all network‑related work organized, clearly labeled, and easy to reference. It contains only the raw PCAP files and the written explanations for each dataset—no demos, scripts, or additional project files—ensuring a clean and focused repository for network analysis and cybersecurity study.
